
		Text::Morse - Encoding and decoding Morse code - v0.07

================================================================================
SYNOPSIS:
================================================================================

  use Text::Morse;

  my $morse = new Text::Morse;
  print scalar($morse->Decode("... --- ..."));
  print scalar($morse->Encode("Adam Bertil"));

================================================================================
INSTALLATION:
================================================================================

    To install this module type the following:

       perl Makefile.PL
       make
       make test
       make install

================================================================================
USAGE:
================================================================================

	Useless but fun.

================================================================================
SEE ALSO:
================================================================================

	/usr/games/morse

